              "free_text": [
                " THE TRITIUM TARGET WAS ABSORBED IN A 0.4 MG/CM2",
                " THICK TITANIUM LAYER, EVAPORATED ON A 0.25 MM THICK",
                " COPPER BACKING. THIS TARGET WAS USED TO PRODUCE",
                " NEUTRONS FROM 14.6 TO 19.9 MEV."
